  "segments": [
    {
      "segmentNumber": 1,
      "visualDescription": "A deep indigo gradient background, softly fading to a slightly lighter blue near the center, with a subtle warm glow emanating from the bottom edge, indicating light under a door. The rest of the space is clean and dark, perfect for text.",
      "dialogueOrNarration": "Leo sat alone in his bedroom. He was only seven years old. The room was very dark, with just a little light coming from under the door. Outside, a faint streetlamp glowed, making long, strange shadows on the wall. Leo's eyes were wide. He felt a small shiver. [anxiously] His hands trembled slightly. [softly] He saw monsters in the shadows, but they were not real. They were only in his mind. He pulled his old teddy bear, Mr. Snuggles, closer to him. Mr. Snuggles was soft and warm. Leo held him tight. He wished for the morning sun. He wished his mom would come and turn on the light. The darkness felt very big and very scary. [with a slight tremor] He just wanted to feel safe. [wistfully]",
      "subtitle": "Leo sat alone in his bedroom. He was only seven years old. The room was very dark, with just a little light coming from under the door. Outside, a faint streetlamp glowed, making long, strange shadows on the wall. Leo's eyes were wide. He felt a small shiver. His hands trembled slightly. He saw monsters in the shadows, but they were not real. They were only in his mind. He pulled his old teddy bear, Mr. Snuggles, closer to him. Mr. Snuggles was soft and warm. Leo held him tight. He wished for the morning sun. He wished his mom would come and turn on the light. The darkness felt very big and very scary. He just wanted to feel safe.\nLeo ngồi một mình trong phòng ngủ. Cậu bé mới bảy tuổi. Căn phòng rất tối, chỉ có một chút ánh sáng lọt qua khe cửa. Bên ngoài, ánh đèn đường mờ nhạt chiếu sáng, tạo ra những bóng đổ dài, kỳ lạ trên tường. Mắt Leo mở to. Cậu bé cảm thấy rùng mình nhẹ. Tay cậu run rẩy khẽ. Cậu nhìn thấy quái vật trong bóng tối, nhưng chúng không có thật. Chúng chỉ ở trong tâm trí cậu. Cậu kéo con gấu bông cũ của mình, Mr. Snuggles, lại gần hơn. Mr. Snuggles mềm mại và ấm áp. Leo ôm chặt nó. Cậu ước mặt trời mọc. Cậu ước mẹ sẽ đến và bật đèn. Bóng tối cảm thấy rất lớn và rất đáng sợ. Cậu chỉ muốn cảm thấy an toàn.",
